If you want to classify, you're either going to be 
involved in the production of a radioactive

00:02.748 --> 00:29.177
substance, if that's your interest, or you're 
going to be involved in looking at the radiation

00:02.748 --> 00:29.177
that comes off the reactor itself, those parts.

