The radiation that comes after the reactor itself 
went down in popularity? Only because of the

00:35.876 --> 00:41.644
completion of studies of particle physics.

00:44.828 --> 00:45.629
That was in the early 70s? Yeah, the effort was so 
intense, as I said, throughout the world, that

00:46.089 --> 00:56.303
they progressed very rapidly.

00:56.323 --> 00:59.687
The intensity definitely fell away. Once the 
information is gathered, the basic information,

01:00.528 --> 01:05.873
it has not changed much. Well, you still have 
people looking, and they'll change numbers a

01:07.635 --> 01:11.879
little bit. You'll see a little change, but not 
