01:15.803 --> 01:29.877
radioactive material or creating advanced codes 
or activating material, has that changed since

01:15.803 --> 01:29.877
you started? Well, it's changed in the fact that I 
think there's more ingenuity in the use of these

01:30.008 --> 01:38.037
materials, particularly the medical field. 
