03:22.379 --> 03:49.483
so easily with a computer so you can feed back 
information in a diagnostic case feed it into a

03:22.379 --> 03:49.483
computer and it will digest all that information 
and give you a very simple answer I think the

03:22.379 --> 03:49.483
electronics has played just as vital part as any 
because the reactors have always been here. The

03:51.712 --> 03:55.596
radioactive materials have always been 
available. It's just that the technology to use

03:57.338 --> 04:04.245
